e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇翼鋒疤真係食得屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講呢？ 皇馬其實都係踢 4312 ，巴利拍賓施馬/c朗係前面，伊斯高踢攻中 ，我認為巴塞都可以參考，特別係美斯踢攻中我認為更出色</blockquote><br />\n呢個4312對閘喺邊路活動嘅要求好高，巴塞啲閘不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有，你估人地唔知美斯踢攻中勁咩<br />\n你放佢打攻中，人地mark死佢，咁佢唯有移入邊線攞波轉身，一定無咁致命<br />\n<br />\n但係，佢踢開嘅翼鋒，佢一變向變速移入中路攞波轉身，要扭要比佢都好致命<br />\n<br />\n你可以話佢咁扭得邊線攞咪邊線攞，如果扭親都有不如擺中堅1打11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb971db4843eeeb73e5fb06a9a008ffbd9e244d","tid":359410,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但摩迪+kroos明顯高現時巴塞中場幾班波<br />\n利申全盛小白另計</blockquote><br />\n之前先有班蝗沖出黎話魔笛同全盛雙核同級架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔係<br />\n柒少陣啦</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n逐個比較可能同級 但雙核個化學作用太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪即係同級囉&hellip;"},{"pid":"4a0a0ba09a13d3d6c4d42b18fe8f7d5f5355e244","tid":359410,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成撚日講簽古天奴<br />\n條友有幾勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔勁架咪撚買呀笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a41db28daad4168fdcbd640a14bd5b5daa5aa71","tid":359410,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但摩迪+kroos明顯高現時巴塞中場幾班波<br />\n利申全盛小白另計</blockquote><br />\n之前先有班蝗沖出黎話魔笛同全盛雙核同級